              This is <m>55.0\, \text{mi/hr} = 0.0246\, \text{km/s}</m>.
              Continue working on the conversion to meters per second.
            </p>
          </feedback>
        </choice>

        <choice correct="no">
          <statement>
            <p>
              <m>88.5\, \text{m/s}</m>
            </p>
          </statement>

          <feedback>
            <p>
              Your enchanted click missed the mark, try again.
              This is <m>55.0\, \text{mi/hr} = 88.5\, \text{km/hr}</m>.
